\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"I've, ah, been assured that it's safe," said the blonde woman.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"So were the girls who worked in the factory," said Lois.
 She wondered how far she was deviating from what Lex had planned.
 Obviously she was intended to walk out of the store with watch and the
