\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
I don't know, Lex wrote back.
 I have reason to believe that it will hurt him.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Lois read the note and frowned at him.
 She tapped her pencil against the paper for a few moments.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
I'm not sure we should.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Lex stifled a groan.
 He was losing Lois, that much was clear now.
