 My own estimates are higher, but you know him better than I do.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Lois frowned.
 Will it depower him, or kill him?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
I don't know, wrote Lex.
 He was halfway certain that she was testing him.
 He would have pivoted, and claimed that he knew what the effect was, but
 he'd already said that he didn't know, and couldn't take the chance of
